findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: Functions includeToWhiteList(), setLimits(), addPrivateSalers(), removePrivateSalers(), addExcludedFromLimits(), removeExcludedFromLimits() and multiSendTokens() use loops that can cause OUT_OF_GAS exception if the input list is too long.
findings.location: Functions includeToWhiteList(), setLimits(), addPrivateSalers(), removePrivateSalers(), addExcludedFromLimits(), removeExcludedFromLimits() and multiSendTokens()
